{"tid":2080172,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(無恥fb)Old news is so......   貼舊文將收 Facebook 警告","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T17:40:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41c1c2cb7909bb5616e049ba20a2ba7ec7db16e9","tid":2080172,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"Facebook 是很多網民的資訊來源，假新聞固然是嚴重問題，有時候就連真新聞亦會造成困擾。有些網民不知道是刻意還是無心，往往會將數年前的新聞重新分享，這樣可能會影響網民對當下發生的事情有不同解讀和誤判。Facebook 似乎亦明白這個問題，剛剛宣佈一項新的解決措施。<br />\n<br />\n當用戶在 Facebook 分享 90 天或以前的舊文章，系統會在分享前發出警告，通知用戶文章是超過 3 個月的舊聞。用戶收到警告後，可以選擇返回前一頁，亦可以堅持繼續發貼分享。Facebook 表示新措施會由即日起，向全球用戶開放，希望藉此可以打擊誤導訊息在其平台流傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27247/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1141%2F27247%2F1%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=79b24603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27247/1/</a>"},{"pid":"096e55a0e762dac75e5edbc166d87195c748d015","tid":2080172,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"facebook <img src=\"https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net/emoticons/v1/245/1.0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-cdn.jtvnw.net%2Femoticons%2Fv1%2F245%2F1.0&h=8b83dbd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"659a038eb4bf8444d413f515aa2218f4d258811f","tid":2080172,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"今時今日係得啲廢老仲用fb"},{"pid":"52bf6deb7bf57c325eb68dc6b3b4624d856b660b","tid":2080172,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}